Package com.clarionmedia.infinitum.orm.relationship

Provides the classes necessary to model entity relationships.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ForeignKeyRelationship This abstract class represents a relationship which relies on a foreign key to make the entity association, such as many-to-one, one-to-many, and one-to-one relationships.
ManyToManyRelationship This class encapsulates a many-to-many relationship between two models.
ManyToOneRelationship This class encapsulates a many-to-one relationship between two models.
ModelRelationship This abstract class is used to define a relationship between two domain entities.
OneToManyRelationship This class encapsulates a one-to-many relationship between two models.
OneToOneRelationship This class encapsulates a one-to-one relationship between two models.
